text: Kholmogory () is a rural locality (a village) in Shabagishsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 121 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km from Yermolayevo, 9 km from Shabagish. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Kholmogory, Republic of Bashkortostan
